                            <h1 id="uchat-mobile-app">
                                <a href="#uchat-mobile-app" class="header-anchor">#</a> Smart ChatBot Mobile App</h1>
                                <p>
                                    Smart ChatBot introduced mobile apps for android &amp; iOS, in this help documentation, we will show you how to use the mobile app with Smart ChatBot seamlessly.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    <img src="../assets/img/uchat-app01.534c3945.png" alt="title">
                                </p>
                                <h2 id="download-the-mobile-app">
                                    <a href="#download-the-mobile-app" class="header-anchor">#</a> 
                                    Download the mobile app
                                </h2>
                                <p>
                                    You can download the mobile app from the link below or search “Smart ChatBot live chat” in AppStore, or search “Smart ChatBot” in Google Play.
